<section id="a">
<div><h2>What is Karrusel</h2>
    <p>Karrusel is 3 days of house, disco, and techno in the magical forest. Karrusel takes place at a secluded green spot on Refshaleøen in central Copenhagen. It is an 18+ event, that takes place in rain or shine.</p>
    <p> Artists subject to change. As the sun sets over the Copenhagen skyline, the festival reaches its crescendo, with electrifying performances igniting the night and  creating unforgettable memories for all who partake. With its vibrant energy and circus spirit, Karrusel Festival continues to captivate the  hearts and minds of Copenhageners and visitors alike, leaving an indelible mark on the cultural landscape of the city.</p></div>
